{"image_id": "CHD_2012_page_102", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "CHURCH & DWIGHT CO., INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [383.3, 158.9, 891.8, 179.7]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [298.1, 196.4, 977.0, 217.2]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2012, there was approximately 125 thousand shares of Common Stock from shares held", "bbox": [204.2, 246.6, 1111.4, 267.4]}, {"text": "as Treasury Stock in a rabbi trust to protect the interest of the directors’ deferred compensation plan participants", "bbox": [162.5, 271.6, 1098.8, 292.4]}, {"text": "in the event of a change of control.", "bbox": [162.5, 296.6, 453.3, 317.4]}, {"text": "14. Stock Based Compensation Plans", "bbox": [162.5, 358.9, 489.6, 379.7]}, {"text": "The Company has options outstanding under four equity compensation plans. Under the Omnibus Equity", "bbox": [204.2, 396.6, 1081.3, 417.4]}, {"text": "Plan, the Company may grant options and other stock-based awards to employees and directors. Under the 1983", "bbox": [162.5, 421.6, 1098.9, 442.4]}, {"text": "Stock Option Plan and the Stock Award Plan, the Company granted options to key management employees.", "bbox": [162.5, 446.6, 1063.2, 467.4]}, {"text": "Under the Stock Option Plan for Directors, the Company granted options to non-employee directors. Following", "bbox": [162.5, 471.6, 1093.1, 492.4]}, {"text": "adoption of the Omnibus Equity Plan by stockholders in 2008, no further grants were permitted under the other", "bbox": [162.5, 496.6, 1090.8, 517.4]}, {"text": "equity compensation plans. Options outstanding under the plans are issued at market value on the date of grant,", "bbox": [162.5, 521.6, 1091.6, 542.4]}, {"text": "vest on the third anniversary of the date of grant and must be exercised within ten years of the date of grant. If,", "bbox": [162.5, 546.6, 1086.5, 567.4]}, {"text": "upon termination of a participant’s employment (other than a termination for cause), a participant is at least 55", "bbox": [162.5, 571.6, 1085.8, 592.4]}, {"text": "years old, has at least five years of service, and the sum of the participant’s age and years of service is at least 65,", "bbox": [162.5, 596.6, 1108.8, 617.4]}, {"text": "the participant may exercise any stock options granted in 2007 or later within a period of three years from the", "bbox": [162.5, 621.6, 1076.7, 642.4]}, {"text": "date of termination or, if earlier, the date such stock options otherwise would have expired, subject to specified", "bbox": [162.5, 646.6, 1088.8, 667.4]}, {"text": "conditions. Issuances of Common Stock to satisfy employee option exercises currently are made from treasury", "bbox": [162.5, 671.6, 1085.9, 692.4]}, {"text": "stock.", "bbox": [162.5, 696.6, 211.7, 717.4]}, {"text": "Stock option transactions for the three years ended December 31, 2012 were as follows:", "bbox": [204.2, 746.6, 937.7, 767.4]}, {"text": "Options", "bbox": [731.0, 841.2, 787.5, 857.9]}, {"text": "(In millions)", "bbox": [715.6, 857.9, 803.1, 874.6]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [823.6, 807.9, 897.7, 824.6]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [830.9, 824.6, 890.2, 841.2]}, {"text": "Exercise", "bbox": [830.5, 841.2, 890.7, 857.9]}, {"text": "Price", "bbox": [842.1, 857.9, 879.1, 874.6]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [924.5, 791.2, 998.5, 807.9]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [931.8, 807.9, 991.0, 824.6]}, {"text": "Remaining", "bbox": [922.6, 824.6, 1000.4, 841.2]}, {"text": "Contractual", "bbox": [918.4, 841.2, 1004.5, 857.9]}, {"text": "Term", "bbox": [941.6, 857.9, 981.4, 874.6]}, {"text": "Aggregate", "bbox": [1032.3, 807.9, 1105.4, 824.6]}, {"text": "Intrinsic", "bbox": [1038.4, 824.6, 1099.6, 841.2]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1048.0, 841.2, 1089.7, 857.9]}, {"text": "(In millions)", "bbox": [1025.3, 857.9, 1112.8, 874.6]}, {"text": "Outstanding at December 31, 2009 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 888.2, 694.8, 909.1]}, {"text": "8.9", "bbox": [749.7, 888.2, 775.7